title: Last Match Didn't count?
body: Ok so I made a post earlier about having the game crash screen after I had finished my ranked game and not being able to get off it. that has been fixed but now the game (that we won) has not been counted. It is not in my match history and I did not gain LP for it. Would like to know what is going on with that.

replies.body: I think you should just edit this into your previous thread.
